Template: shared/config
Type: select
Choices: mainnet, testnet, regtest
Description: Choose a configuration environment to run your node.
 .
 Choose the environment you want to configure to run your node.
 .
  * Mainnet: Your node will run against mainnet network.
 .
  * Testnet: Your node will run against testnet network.
 .
  * Regtest: Your node will run against regtest network.
 .
 NOTE: To reconfigure your node once installed, you need to change the symbolic link located in /etc/rsk.
